---
description: Retry failed loads (fetches, requests) before giving up
alwaysApply: true
---

# Retry before giving up

When something doesn't load the first time (e.g. URL fetch times out, request fails), **try again a few times** (e.g. 2–3 retries with a short pause or immediately) before treating it as unavailable or using a fallback. Don't give up after a single failure.
